review.description:
The space is great with the high ceiling and natural lights. 
Came in at a Sunday noon. 
Laptopers and other people co-exited in the space. Pros: 
many seats; 
many outlets; 
decent coffee; 
decent wifi;
Food is great! Tried the avocado toast for lunch. 

Cons: really LOUD!
Someone had a birthday party with cakes and songs. 

Ps: I don't like beer but many people get bear while working on laptops.
